		<div class="icon-row">
			<a data-share-service="mail" data-share-loc="modal" href="mailto:?subject=Naomi Klein is right: Unchecked capitalism will destroy civilization&body=http://grist.org/climate-energy/naomi-klein-is-right-unchecked-capitalism-will-destroy-civilization/" class="btn-pill addthis_button_email" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><i class="sprite-share-lg-email"></i></a> 
			<a data-share-service="more" data-share-loc="modal" href="http://api.addthis.com/oexchange/0.8/offer?url=http%3A%2F%2Fgrist.org%2Fclimate-energy%2Fnaomi-klein-is-right-unchecked-capitalism-will-destroy-civilization%2F&title=Naomi+Klein+is+right%3A+Unchecked+capitalism+will+destroy+civilization&description=Klein%27s+new+book%2C+%22This+Changes+Everything%3A+Capitalism+vs.+the+Climate%2C%22+argues+that+it%27s+now+too+late+for+incremental+steps+to+fight+climate+change.+We+have+go+big.&pubid=ra-4dc04d5824409f84" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="btn-pill addthis_button_more"><i class="sprite-share-lg-more"></i></a> 
